name: In The Middle (DistortedCube)
description: My first ever game that I made in a week for the Brackeys Game Jam 2023. It's all about how sometimes things end for a good reason and it's not the end, it's the beginning of something new and beautiful. I have had no prior experience making any sort of video games, but I really wanted to push myself out of my comfort zone and create something that was decent enough to be played. Have fun playing!
